| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3969 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0b0a6ed2-c3fb-5e6b-aa25-a2d347fc8ec2"
